734
01:08:12,928 --> 01:08:21,192
Try to time your snow removal in your private driveway to line up with the plow pass if you can.

735
01:08:23,089 --> 01:08:30,553
You know you shouldn't be pushing or plowing or snow blowing your snow from your driveway into the road that usually just makes things worse for your neighbor.

736
01:08:32,374 --> 01:08:41,860
